NeuroGenesis4

NeuroGenesis4.Rd

A list of 4 neuro data sets sampled, containing: Meissner.inVitro.bulk.Hs, LIBD.AZ.inVitro.bulk.Hs, Geschwind.inVivo.sc.Hs, Jabaudon.inVivo.sc.Mm

data(NeuroGenesis4)

Format

A list containing 4 dataframes

Examples


data(NeuroGenesis4)
